data.description: **OPEN HOUSE SATURDAY, OCTOBER 14TH FROM 11:00 AM TO 2:00 PM!**  Introducing a stunning and spacious home where luxury, comfort, and modern design seamlessly blend to create a haven of elegance and tranquility. Upon entering this 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathrooms home, you are immediately greeted by an expansive open-concept living area that effortlessly combines the kitchen, dining, and living spaces. Soaring ceilings and strategically placed windows flood the interior with an abundance of natural light, creating an inviting and airy atmosphere. Beautiful tile floors throughout the main living areas lend warmth and sophistication to the space.  The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, a center island with a breakfast bar, and ample cabinet space. It's the ideal setting for preparing meals while still being part of the conversation happening in the adjacent living and dining areas.  The back door opens onto an expansive covered patio, seamlessly merging indoor and outdoor living where you can relax or barbecue. The master suite boasts a spacious bedroom with oversized windows. The en-suite bathroom is beautiful with a soaking tub, a separate glass-enclosed shower, dual vanities, and a huge walk-in closet providing a spa-like experience right at home.  Enjoy the amenities which include a pool, fitness center, playground, firepit, dog park and walking trails!
